<style>
	.row{
		width: 100%;
		margin-bottom: 10px;
	}
	.row.pull-right{
		text-align: right;
	}

	.pull-right{
		margin-right: 0;
	}

	.flag{
		display: inline-block;
		width: 45px;
		height: 30px;
		background-color: grey; 
		cursor: pointer;
		background-position: -3px -12px;
		background-size: 48px 51px;
	}

	.flag.vi{
		background-image: url('images/flag-vn.png'); 
	}

	.flag.en{
		background-image: url('images/flag-uk.png'); 
	}
.intro{
	margin-top: 22px !important;
}
.card-title{
	padding: 10px;
	position: absolute;
	top: 0;
	left: 0;
	transition: all 2s;
}
.card .ripper{
	background-color: #263740;
}
.card.dream .card-icon{
	border-radius: 0; 
}
.card.osource .card-icon{
	background-color: #263740; 
}
	.intro .avatar{
		margin-left: 0;
		display: inline-block;
		width: 128px;
		height: 128px;
	}
	.intro .text{
		padding-left: 20px;
		display: inline-block;
		vertical-align: top;
		width: 552px;
	}
	.intro .text p{
		margin: 0;
	}
	.pulzee{
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: row;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		margin-top: 20px;
	}
	.quater{
		width: 50%;
	}
	.card{
		border: solid 1px #eceff2;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.card .card-header{
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		height: 120px;
		overflow: hidden;	
		text-align: center;	
	}

	.card:hover .card-header .ripper{
		opacity: 1;
		transform: scale(10);
	}
	.card:hover .card-header .card-title{
		color: white;
	}
	.card-header .ripper{
		position: absolute;
		top: 10px;
		left: 10px;
		opacity: 0;
		transition: all 2s;
	}
.card-title .text{
    vertical-align: top;
    line-height: 52px;
    font-size: 24px;

}

.card-icon, .card-title .text{
	display: inline-block !important;
	margin-left: 15px;
}
	.card-icon, .card .card-header .ripper{
		width: 100px;
    	height: 100px;
	    border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.card-body{
		padding: 10px;
		margin-top: 0px !important; 
	}

@media(max-width: 799px){
	.intro .avatar{
		display: block;
		margin-right: auto;
		margin-left: auto;		
	}
	.intro .text{
		width: 100%;
		padding-left: 0;
	}
}

@media(max-width: 600px){
	.quater{
		width: 100%;
	}	
}

</style>
<div class="row pull-right" style="margin-bottom: 20px">
	<div class="pull-right">
		<span class="flag vi" title="switch to Vietnamese"></span>
		<span class="flag en" title="switch to English"></span>
	</div>
</div>
<br>
<blockquote class="intro">
<img class="avatar no-fancy" src="images/avatar.png" title="xin cho, ti l Minh" />
<div class="text">
	<p>Xin Cho ti tn l <strong>Lc Vn Minh</strong>, ti l mt ngi trm tnh it ni v li nhc . Cuc i i vi ti kh n c <strong>gia nh</strong>, c <strong>bn b</strong> l c tt c,  cn cn c <strong>mng</strong> na ch nh. am m ln nht ca ti l <strong>lp trnh</strong>, v ti qut nh ginh c tui thanh xun  theo ui am m ca mnh, t nhng dng code ca mnh ti hy vng s gp phn cho th gii tt p hn.</p>
</div>
</blockquote>
<div class="row pulzee">
	<div class="quater card life">
		<div class="card-header">
		<div class="ripper">
		</div>
		<div class="card-title">
		<img src="images/flat-faces-icons-circle-3.png" alt="my life" class="card-icon no-fancy">
		<h4 class="text">V Cuc Sng</h4>
		</div>
		</div>
		<p class="card-body">
			Cuc sng ca ti kh n gin, ngoi lp trnh th v thi gian rnh ti thng <strong>lt eb</strong> tm hiu s tnh giang h, cc <strong>cng ng mi</strong> cng nh <trong>hackernews</trong>. vi cc hot offline, ti thch <strong>n</strong> v thch nu n, <trong>c sch</trong>. mn th tao yu thch ca ti l <strong>chy b</strong> v <strong>bi li</strong>, c l ti khng gii mn no khc :).
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="quater card dream">
		<div class="card-header">
		<div class="ripper">
		</div>
		<div class="card-title">
		<img src="images/Creative-Tail-rocket.svg.png" alt="dream" class="card-icon no-fancy">
		<h4 class="text">V ng Lc</h4>
		</div>
		</div>
		<div class="card-body">
			Ti lun mun hc hi nhng <strong>iu mi m</strong>, i ln nhng <strong>vng t mi</strong>, tr nghip nhng nn <strong>vn ha mi</strong> v nm th nhng <strong>mn n mi</strong>. vi cng vic ti lun mun hon thin <strong>k nng</strong> cng nh <strong>tu duy</strong> ca mnh  mi sn phm ca mnh u <strong>chm n tri tim ca ngi dng</strong>. 
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="quater card code">
		<div class="card-header">
		<div class="ripper">
		</div>
		<div class="card-title">
		<img src="images/monitor_code__editor-512.png" alt="coding" class="card-icon no-fancy">
		<h4 class="text">V Lp Trnh</h4>
		</div>
		</div>
		<div class="card-body">
			Ti c mt nim am m vi <strong>lp trnh</strong> ni chung v <strong>lp trnh web</strong> ni ring. Ti thch s tin li ca <strong>PHP</strong>, yu  s n nh ca <strong>java</strong>,  yu s mm do ca <strong>javascript</strong>, s mnh m ca <strong>python</strong>, s n gin ca <strong>ruby</strong>. ngoi ra ti cng thch nhng front-end frameworks nh <strong>React</strong>, <strong>Angular 2</strong>, <strong>Polymer</strong>. mi trng lp trnh yu thch ca ti l <strong>Linux</strong> v cc IDE ca <strong>JetBrain</strong>.
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="quater card osource">
		<div class="card-header"> 
		<div class="ripper">
		</div>
		<div class="card-title">
		<img src="images/github-icon.png" alt="open-source" class="card-icon no-fancy">
		<h4 class="text">V M Ngun M</h4>
		</div>
		</div>
		<div class="card-body">
			Tt nhin ri, ti yu m ngun m v gnh c ngy trn <strong>github</strong>. Tht hnh phc khi c ng gp cho nhng d n tuyt vi nh <strong>LearnPress</strong> ..., ti sn sng tham gia vo cc d n m ngun m  ngha, cho i cng l nhn li, v mt cng ng m ngn m ln mnh.
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
{% endraw %}

## Ch Mc
di u l nhng trang eb ti thng xuyn lui ti, y  nhng ngun thng tin khng l gip ti gii tr cng nh hon thin bn thn mnh hn.

- [medium](http://medium.com)  tt c trn mt trang duy nht
- [wait but why](http://waitbutwhy.com/)  nhn cc sng qua mt gc nhn mi
- [Freecodecamp](https://medium.freecodecamp.com/)   mt cng ng nng ng v t v
- [hackernews](https://news.ycombinator.com/)  tng hp tin tc cng ngh
- [TED](https://www.ted.com/)  ni chia s nhng cu chuyn  ngha, nhng  tng kit sut
- [Javascript sence](https://medium.com/javascript-scene)  mi kha cnh ca javascript
- [techtalk](http://techtalk.vn/)   tin tc cng ngh tiwngs vit
- [toidicodedao](toidicodedao.com)  nhng cu chuyn chn thc v cuc sng ca lp trnh vin
- [daynhauhoc](https://daynhauhoc.com)    din n trao i v cng ngh

