khi cn phi ni nhiu on code trn ng l ``shit code`` th thit ri, kh c kh maintain nu v tnh c c th cng ch th hiu l on ny lm mc ch g, vy c cch no  gii qut vn  ny khng?

## Water Fall callback

cch du tin ti ngh n chnh l  ``Water Fall callback``, n gin l chia callback ra nhiu hm ri ln luwowit ci trc gi ci sau :).

cch ny ch l mt cch vit khc so vi hell n trn tuy l c clear hn oi cht nhng xem ra vn khng ci thin nhiu v mt maintain code sau ny.

```javascript

	function task1(){
		console.log('task 1')
		setTimeout(task2, 500)
	}

	function task2(){
		console.log('task 2')
		setTimeout(task3, 600)
	}

	function task3(callback){
		console.log('task 3')
		setTimeout(task4, 700)
	}

	function task4(callback){
		console.log('task 4')
	}

	task1()
```

## Promisse

``Promisse`` l  mt cch kh trit   x l Callback hell,  mt promisse s nh ngha mt tc v bt ng b vi hai phng thc c bn l ``resolve`` [docs](https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise) (hay fullfill )  bo tc v thnh cng ``reject` var then  thc hin tc v tip theo    ch tc v tht bi.

ta s x l 4 tc v trn vi promisse nh sau:

```javascript

var tasks = new Promise(function(resolve, reject){
	setTimeout(resolve, 500)
})

tasks.then(function(){
	console.log('task 1')
})
.then(function(){
	return new Promise(function(resolve, reject){
		setTimeout(resolve, 600)
	})
})
.then(function(){
	console.log('task 2')
})
.then(function(){
	return new Promise(function(resolve, reject){
		setTimeout(resolve, 700)
	})
})
.then(function(){
	console.log('task 3')
})
.then(function(){
	return new Promise(function(resolve, reject){
		setTimeout(resolve, 800)
	})
})
.then(function(){
	console.log('task 4')
})

```

c v hi di dng ngh :D, nhng thay vo  ta s c mt code flow cc k r rng ta s d dng debug cng nh ddowcj on code ny, n s i 500ms ri log ra **task 1** sau  i 600ms ri log ra **task 2** v.v.. thc s vn  Callback hell  c gii qut. nhng vn  l c php hi di dng mt cht, nhng nh pht trin JavaScript cng nhn ra iu ny v a ra nhng ci tin ln  l ``generater function``  phin bn **ES6** v ``async/await`` vi ``ES6+``

## generater function

nu bn mun hiu r hn v ``generater function`` mi c qua bi vit [ny](/2016/11/18/Ban-da-thuc-su-hieu-generator-function/) ca ti.

vi gi php ny code ca chng ta s d nhn hn kh nhiu, ni mt cch d hiu y nh mt cch  pause hm li v resume li sau mi ln goi next, y qu thc l mt chc nng mnh m khng ch vi 


y l mt tnh nng ca ES6 nn mnh s dng c php ES6 lun nh.

```javascript

function delay(ms){
	return new Promise((res, rej) => {setTimeout(res, ms)})
}

function *doTasks(){
	yield delay(500)
	console.log('task 1')

	yield delay(600)
	console.log('task 2')

	yield delay(700)
	console.log('task 3')

	yield delay(800)
	console.log('task 4')
}

let tasks = doTasks();

while (!tasks.done) tasks.next()

```

kh l gn g :D nhng vn cha phi s mt, xin trn trn gii thiu ``async/await``

## async/await

y l mt tnh nng mi ca ``ES7``, khng cn phi ni nhiu lm g on code sau s ni ln tt c :D

```javascript

function doTask1(){
	setTimeout(() => {
		console.log('task 1')
	}, 500)
}

function doTask2(){
	setTimeout(() => {
		console.log('task 2')
	}, 600)
}

function doTask3(){
	setTimeout(() => {
		console.log('task 3')
	}, 500)


function doTask4(){
	console.log('task 4')
}



sync function doTasks() {
  await doTask1()
  await doTask2()
  await doTask3()
  await doTask4()
}

doTasks()

```

trn y mnh  gii thiu mi vi cch c bn  gii quyt callback hell, hy vng gip ch c cho ai cn.

