{% asset_img "javascript-generator-funtion.png" "javascript generator function" %}

Hello anh em, hnh nh blog cha c bi vit no v [#ES6](/tags/es6) c hm nay mnh s qut nh vit v **generator function** v thnh tht m ni mnh cng cha thc s hiu thng ny lm :3, tin y mnh s gii thiu mt s ng dng cng nh tim nng ca tnh nng ny trong cc tc vu thc t. 

<!--more-->

## ci nhn u tin 

Mt trong nhng tnh nng mnh thy t v nht trong **ES6 -  ECMAScript 2015** chnh l **generator function**, khi lt qua cc tnh nng ca ES6 v bt gp tnh nng ny suy ngh u tin trong u mnh chnh l...

> ci WTF g th, bc [Allen Wirfs-Brock](http://www.wirfs-brock.com/allen/about) ng l rnh ri, ti sao li sng to ra ci th ny trong khi callback vi promisse l lm async tt ri, iteritor th for vi while l c, ci my pht in ny ch phi l  b i hay sao. trong khi tnh hnh tnh hnh giang h ang lon tin phn tm nh nh ny bt hc c ci g thi hay ci  :'(

hm nay do qua mt vng google thy ci th b i ny cng li hi ra pht.  tm hiu ti sao li c ci ny mnh s i t n tng ca n, **iterator**.

## Iterator
**Iterator** chnh l th m ai cng dng nhng khng phi ai cng bit n n (ng tin n la y >:( ), cng ging trong cc ngn ng khc **iterator** l mt i tng dng  truy cp vo mt dy cc phn t, mi ln n s tr li ph t tip theo trong dy v gi  c t t duyt mi ln n c gi n. **javascript iterator** l mt i tng cung cp phng thc ``next()`` tr li mt i tng gm hai thuc tnh l ``done`` kim tra xem dy  duyt ht cha v ``value`` ga tr phn t tip theo trong dy.

```javascript
function makeIterator(array){
    var nextIndex = 0;

    return {
       next: function(){
           return nextIndex < array.length ?
               {value: array[nextIndex++], done: false} :
               {done: true};
       }
    }
}

```

Mt khi  c khi to chng ta c th gi ``next``  duyt qua thng tip theo.

```javascript

var it = makeIterator(['one', 'to',]);
console.log(it.next().value); // 'one'
console.log(it.next().value); // 'two'
console.log(it.next().done);  // true

```

Thy quen quen cha no? chun cm m nu ri, y chnh chnh l cha  ca ``function *`` ch g na B-).

![](200w.gif)

## Generator

**Iterator** l mt pattern thc s hu dng nhng kh lt lo trong ci t v khng d dng  maintain c cc trng ti ca n, n y mi thy ng l **JS** ang thiu mt c php chun cho pattrens ny n khai thc ht tim nng ca n, v... ,  vng xin trn trng gii thiu **Generator function** cn c bit n vi bit danh ``function *`` hay ``yield function``:

 ```javascript

function* idMaker(){
  var index = 0;
  while(true)
    yield index++;
}

var gen = idMaker();

console.log(gen.next().value); // 0
console.log(gen.next().value); // 1
console.log(gen.next().value); // 2

```
c th hiu **generator** l mt loi function to ra **iterator**, mt function c gi l **generator** nu bn trong c cha mt hay nhiu biu thc ``yield`` v c khai bo bng t kha ``function *``: 

```javascript

var myIterable = {}
myIterable[Symbol.iterator] = function* () {
    yield 1;
    yield 2;
    yield 3;
};

for(let value of myIterable){ 
    console.log(value); 
}

//hay

[...myIterable] // [1, 2, 3]

```
{% pullquote "full tip" %}
nu trong ``function *`` c nhiu gi tr ``yield`` th mi ln gi ``next()`` biu thc ``yield`` tip theo s c thc hin, ging nh l hm b ng bng li ch ln gi ``next`` tip theo vy. s dng ci ny m trn lan th c th dn n kh debug v qun l state, hy th tng tng trong hm ca bn c vi lnh **lp**, vi lnh **r nhanh** v vi ci ``yield`` th...  
{% endpullquote %}

![](vut.gif)

## Built-in iterables
Cn nh  trn mnh ni l bn dng **iterator** ri khng 8-), khng ng u nh, bn khng ch dng ri m cn dng n hng ngy na. cc i tng trong javavascript nh ``String``, ``Array``, ``TypedArray``, ``Map`` v ``Set`` u c built-in iterables  duyt cc phn t, bi v ``prototype`` ca cc i tng ny u c  phng thc ``Symbol.iterator``.

### cc biu thc vi iterables
mt vi biu thc thao tc vi **iterator** bao gm vng lp **for-of**, **spread operator**, **yield**, v **destructuring assignment**.

```javascript

for(let value of ["a", "b", "c"]){
    console.log(value)
}
// "a"
// "b"
// "c"

[..."abc"] // ["a", "b", "c"]

function* gen(){
  yield* ["a", "b", "c"]
}

gen().next() // { value:"a", done:false }

[a, b, c] = new Set(["a", "b", "c"])
a // "a"

```

###  yield*

cng nh ``function *`` ni chung l thng no c c thm cai **"*"** l nh cm c trong tay ri c n tay ai ngi  pht thi :D. biu thc ``yield`` nhn vo mt ``iterator`` khc hoc mt mng khi chy n n s ln lt chy qua cc gi tr ca ``yield*`` ri mi ti cc ``yield`` tip theo.

```javascript

function* fn1(i){
	yield i + 10;
	yield i + 20;
	yield i + 30;
}

function* fn2(){
	var i = 1;	
	yield i;
	yield* fn1(i);
	yield i +1;

}

var gen = fn2();

[...gen] //[1, 11, 21, 31, 2]

```

ni nm na th n c v ging vi callback :D.

## Kt Lun
 thi  thay cho li kt mnh xin a ra mt s ng dng thc t ca thng ny nh:

### 1Async / Await
bn  nghe n  async/await cha, nu cha th hy tp lm qun i v tnh nng ny s c a vo ES7 y, v tin mnh i, n thc s ng ng tin bt go y:

code ca bn t th ny

```javascript

const fetchSomething = () => new Promise((resolve) => {
  setTimeout(() => resolve('future value'), 500);
});

const promiseFunc = () => new Promise((resolve) => {
  fetchSomething().then(result => {
    resolve(result + ' 2');
  });
});

promiseFunc().then(res => console.log(res));

```

s bin thnh th ny: 

```javascript


const fetchSomething = () => new Promise((resolve) => {
  setTimeout(() => resolve('future value'), 500);
});

async function asyncFunction() {
  const result = await fetchSomething(); // returns promise

  // waits for promise and uses promise result
  return result + ' 2';
}

asyncFunction().then(result => console.log(result));

```

### mt cht tng tc

mt trong nhng im th v ca **generator**  l hm next c th nhn li mt i s  qut nh nn lm g tip theo, bn s thch v d ny cho m xem <3 :

```javascript

function* crossBridge() {
  const reply = yield 'What is your favorite color?';
  console.log(reply);
  if (reply !== 'yellow') return 'Wrong!'
  return 'You may pass.';
}

{
  const iter = crossBridge();
  const q = iter.next().value; // Iterator yields question
  console.log(q);
  const a = iter.next('blue').value; // Pass reply back into generator
  console.log(a);
}

// What is your favorite color?
// blue
// Wrong!


{
  const iter = crossBridge();
  const q = iter.next().value;
  console.log(q);
  const a = iter.next('yellow').value;
  console.log(a);
}

// What is your favorite color?
// yellow
// You may pass.

```

### Generator + Promise

mt s kt hp hon ho, c l no 2 th ny sinh ra  ginh co nhau:

```javascript


const isPromise = (obj) => typeof obj !== 'undefined' &&
  typeof obj.then === 'function';

const next = (iter, callback, prev = undefined) => {
  const item = iter.next(prev);
  const value = item.value;

  if (item.done) return callback(prev);

  if (isPromise(value)) {
    value.then(val => {
      setImmediate(() => next(iter, callback, val));
    });
  } else {
    setImmediate(() => next(iter, callback, value));
  }
};

const gensync = (fn) =>
    (...args) => new Promise(resolve => {
  next(fn(...args), val => resolve(val));
});



/* How to use gensync() */

const fetchSomething = () => new Promise((resolve) => {
  setTimeout(() => resolve('future value'), 500);
});

const asyncFunc = gensync(function* () {
  const result = yield fetchSomething(); // returns promise

  // waits for promise and uses promise result
  yield result + ' 2';
});

// Call the async function and pass params.
asyncFunc('param1', 'param2', 'param3')
  .then(val => console.log(val)); // 'future value 2'

```

### Observables v cn nhiu na......

