### s dng require.js

[Requirejs](http://requirejs.org/) l mt cng c  JavaScript file and module loader chy trn trnh duyt khi s dng ta chi cn mt cht config v ng dn n cc module khi ta require module no n s t ng load module  vo trnh duyt. Nghe c c v mi th  hon ho ch tr mt hn ch n l hiu nng vn cha tt nu ta chia cc module qu nh.

### s dng webpack

V ri Nodejs ra i vi [commonjs]() (mt version ca requirejs chy trn node) v [systemjs](https://github.com/systemjs/systemjs) mt module loader khc h tr ES6, u tin cc cng c module loader ny to ra  phc c ng dng Nodejs server side nhng v bn cht ng dng backend hay front end vit bng js l hon taonf ging nhau v hon on c th dng cc module loader ny  build ng dng front-end ging nh lm vi back-end vy.

