<!--more-->

# plugin l kh g?

Ni th ch plugin chc khng l g ri, in hnh nh cc th loi trnh duyt ph bin nh Chrome, Firefox, Opera kiu g mi ci ch ci mt ng plugin n khi trnh duyt c g bt thng li ch li u my thng plugin ra kim ra u tin. mt cch n gin th Plugin chnh l mt b phn mm ci t  h tr, m rng chc nng cho mt phn mm ng dng ln hn, da trn nhng giao thc v API do phn mm ln cung cp.

# plugin c g hay ho?

Kin trc plugin thc s rt tuyt vi, n cho php m rng (thp ch l thay i) cc chc nng ca cc host applications (tm gi l ng dng ch i), vi mt thit k tt cc ng dng c th cm thm bao nhiu chc nng ty thch mi  plugin mang n mt tin ch dn n kh nng m rng ca h thng l cc k tuyt vi mnh xin php c nhai li mt ln na l phi thit k cho tt nh khng l ng ng li tm lum . 

Vi cng ng m ngun m pht trin nh v bo ngy nay, vi mt ng dng c base tt v mt plugin API ti th tc  pht trin s khng th tin ni. VD nh [slack](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=B6zVzWU95Sw) mt h thng nhn tin v trao i cng vic ang rt ni tuy cng ch mi pht trin c vi nm nhng s lng plugin  trong kho ca slack  rt khng l hu ht l do cc bn th ba pht trin, thc s nng gi tr ca ng dng ban u ln gp nhiu ln m mt team khng th lm ht c.

# ri, th ci t thng ny th no?

i vi cc script language nh Javascript, PHP, python... vi dc im mi ln chy l mt ln **thng** dch th c v khng gp tr ngi g ch vic dng mt thng callback hay closure l xong ci ny mnh s ni n vo mt ngy p tri khng xa. vi java cu chuyn c v khng d dng nh th, java 8 mi ra mt tnh nng [Thinking](http://www.linuxtopia.org/online_books/programming_books/thinking_in_java/TIJ310_019.htm) cho php ci t callback & closure mt cch kh d dng cn cc ver thp hn th khng c ci g tng t c, mnh th g java nn cng thy v ny hi khoai.

![application architecture](application-architecture.png)

V c bn  c th cm c plugin th ng dng phi c kin trc n gin nht nh trong hnh trn, hai thnh phn c bn  l application core v plugin manager:
	- **application core:** thng ny l ng dng ch c nhim b bo m logic ca h thng, thc hin cc tc v v hook (gi) cc plugin thc hin nhim v ca mnh trong runtime.
	- **plugins manager:** thng chu s ch o ca thng core c nhim v ng k cc plugin thm, g, bt, tt cc plugin.

 c th cm c plugin ta phi c mt plugin interface y l giao din m tt c cc plugin s k tha, plugin manager s load cc plugins v initial (nm na l to ra thc th ca mi plugin) vo trong mt List cc plugins ri t  application core s ln lt mc ra t ci mt v bt n thc hin nhim v nht nh.

H, mnh gii thch c chui qu chc ko ai hiu ni nh.  trc quan sinh ng mi ae xem v d bn di.

# v d trc quan n

 v d ny mnh s to mt ng dng n gin vi u vo l 1 s, cc plugin s c thm vo  ch bin s   a ra kt qu cui cng cng tr nhn chia g . 

Ok, u tin chng ta phi c mt thng interface chung cho cc plugins. tm gi l ``PluginFunction.java`` i.

```java
public interface PluginFunction {

	// let the application pass in a parameter
	public void setParameter (int param);

	// retrieve a result from the plugin
	public int getResult();

	// return the name of this plugin
	public String getPluginName();

	// can be called to determine whether the plugin
	// aborted execution due to an error condition
	public boolean hasError();
}
```
Tip theo ta phi c mt ci main  chy logic ca ng dng v gi cc plugin, ta gi l ``PluginDemo.java`` cha hm main.

```java
import java.io.File;
import java.util.*;

public class PluginDemo {
	//parameter for plugins
	int count;

	// the directory where we keep the plugin classes
	String pluginsDir;

	// a list where we keep an initialized object of each plugin class
	List plugins;

	public static void main (String args[]) {
		PluginDemo demo = new PluginDemo(args);
		demo.getPlugins();
		demo.runPlugins();
	}

	PluginDemo (String args[]) {
		if (args.length > 0)
			count = Integer.parseInt(args[0]);
		else
			count = 1;

		if (args.length > 1)
			pluginsDir = args[0];
		else
			pluginsDir = "plugins";

		plugins = new ArrayList();

		System.setSecurityManaghttps://analytics.google.com/analytics/web/?authuser=0#croverview/cr-overview/a79213161w118319613p123773431/er(new PluginSecurityManager(pluginsDir));
	}

	protected void getPlugins() {
		File dir = new File(System.getProperty("user.dir") + File.separator + pluginsDir);
		ClassLoader cl = new PluginClassLoader(dir);
		if (dir.exists() && dir.isDirectory()) {
			// we'll only load classes directly in this directory -
			// no subdirectories, and no classes in packages are recognized
			String[] files = dir.list();
			for (int i=0; i<files.length; i++) {
				try {
					// only consider files ending in ".class"
					if (! files[i].endsWith(".class"))
						continue;

					Class c = cl.loadClass(files[i].substring(0, files[i].indexOf(".")));
					Class[] intf = c.getInterfaces();
					for (int j=0; j<intf.length; j++) {
						if (intf[j].getName().equals("PluginFunction")) {
							// the following line assumes that PluginFunction has a no-argument constructor
							PluginFunction pf = (PluginFunction) c.newInstance();
							plugins.add(pf);
							continue;
						}
					}
				} catch (Exception ex) {
					System.err.println("File " + files[i] + " does not contain a valid PluginFunction class.");
				}
			}
		}
	}

	protected void runPlugins() {
		Iterator iter = plugins.iterator();
		while (iter.hasNext()) {
			PluginFunction pf = (PluginFunction) iter.next();
			try {
				pf.setParameter(count);
				System.out.print(pf.getPluginName());
				System.out.print(" ( "+count+" ) = ");
				if (pf.hasError()) {
					System.out.println("there was an error during plugin initialization");
					continue;
				}
				int result = pf.getResult();
				if (pf.hasError())
					System.out.println("there was an error during plugin execution");
				else
					System.out.println(result);
				count++;
			} catch (SecurityException secEx) {
				System.err.println("plugin '"+pf.getClass().getName()+"' tried to do something illegal");
			}
		}
	}
}

```
Ta thy trong hm ``getPlugins`` c mt vng for  load ht cc class m c interface l ``PluginFunction`` ri to ra mt thc th ca class  v lu vo mng ``plugins``. Sau  hm ``runPlugins`` s duyt qua tt c cc plugins set tham s chy hm run ca tng plugin v in ra kt qu.

Ngoi ra hm ``getPlugins`` cn c mt iu th v na chnh l dng setSecurityManager, v y l cc plugins c lp vi h thng nn ta phhair xt qun hn cho n ch nh thanh nin no vui tnh li cho ci plugin xa ht h iu hnh th ch bit ngi y m khc thi .


